[b][size=2]Skyrim is a peaceful World, 
Then the labyrn came to skyrim to have some fun ,
but it become worst , nords and labryn are more alike but they hate each other.
Labryn worship jill as their god , 
Jill is the leader of all labyrn, Half Demon half human, Half normal half psycho. 
That\'s why labryn\'s are psycho.[/b][/size]

[b][size=2]Jill is hiding in skyrm , he have the powerful dagger crafted by gods~ Clues are on the picture[/b][/size]

[img]http://i1172.photobucket.com/albums/r569/davidjohn1234/th_68084a65.jpg[/img]
